title: (x) Enjoy Graphics/Best - Cutout, Bebedot/Cooper Black {Stephen}
content:
I think the first ones are custom / handmade, for sure..   
The 'Enjoy Graphics' one has been created by [KITCHEN](http://web.archive.org/web/20050518124803/http:/kitchen.free.fr/)..   
   
( If you want to create such self-made-hand-made-looking type, the best thing would probably be to create it by hand, to achieve a rather similar style.. )   
   
Sorry, for not being able to really help you..   
I dont really remember seeing any typefaces like these..
author: formlos

comments.content: Those first examples look like someone took an Xacto knife to some construction paper.
